<cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">詩</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">秋夕寄友僧</cb:mulu><cb:div type="other">
<milestone unit="juan" n="45"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0931c11"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0931c12"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0931c13"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184a05"/><cb:juan fun="open" n="45"><cb:mulu type="卷" n="45"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead>閑居編第四十五</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="X" n="0931c14"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0931c15"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184a06"/><byline cb:type="author">宋孤山沙門　智圓　著</byline>
<lb ed="X" n="0931c16"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184a07"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">陳宮</cb:mulu><head>陳宮</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0931c17"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184a08"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0931c1701"><l>龍盤虎踞景堪尋<caesura/>王氣消亡信禍淫</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0931c18"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184a09"/><l>結綺臨春何處是<caesura/>數聲啼鳥暮煙深</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0931c19"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184a10"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">春日別同志</cb:mulu><head>春日別同志</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0931c20"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184a11"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0931c2001"><l>路岐南北與東西<caesura/>竚立遲遲惜解擕</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0931c21"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184a12"/><l>忍向離亭折楊柳<caesura/><g ref="#CB15085"/>花零落杜<g ref="#CB15102"/>啼</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0931c22"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184a13"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">夏日湖上寄太白長老</cb:mulu><head>夏日湖上寄太白長老</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0931c23"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184a14"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0931c2301"><l>風撼芙蕖入座香<caesura/>水軒閑坐趣何長</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0931c24"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184a15"/><l>相懷不是人間景<caesura/>隔岸歸禽噪晚涼</l></lg></cb:div>
<pb ed="X" xml:id="X56.0949.0932a" n="0932a"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a01"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184a16"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">西湖</cb:mulu><head>西湖</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a02"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184a17"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0932a0201"><l>清帶月華涵竹戶<caesura/>冷澄秋色照禪衣</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a03"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184a18"/><l>滔滔潤物知多少<caesura/>極目寒波瀁落暉</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a04"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184b01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">送禪者</cb:mulu><head>送禪者</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a05"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184b02"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0932a0501"><l>祖意曾明萬事閑<caesura/>誰云方外與人間</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a06"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184b03"/><l>卷衣江上秋來別<caesura/>處處禪心朵朵山</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a07"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184b04"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">古意</cb:mulu><head>古意</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a08"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184b05"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0932a0801"><l>登山伐樵柯忽折<caesura/>臨井汲泉綆仍絕</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a09"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184b06"/><l>音信不來無處說<caesura/>朔風飄飄滿天雪</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a10"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184b07"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">雲</cb:mulu><head>雲</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a11"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184b08"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0932a1101"><l>冷照碧潭閑不極<caesura/>靜當青漢影彌分</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a12"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184b09"/><l>卷舒終合為霖雨<caesura/>不向陽臺惑楚君</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a13"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184b10"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">苔錢三首</cb:mulu><head>苔錢三首</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a14"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184b11"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0932a1401"><l>夷甫不言非爾類<caesura/>魯<g ref="#CB17051"/>為論偶同名</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a15"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184b12"/><l>秋來自滿虗閑地<caesura/>不用良工鼓鑄成</l></lg>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a16"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184b13"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">其一</cb:mulu><head>其一</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a17"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184b14"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0932a1701"><l>求多未必增貪<g ref="#CB15137"/><caesura/>委積唯堪貰寂寥</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a18"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184b15"/><l>顏子黔婁舊居畔<caesura/>亂鋪平地伴逍遙</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a19"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184b16"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">其二</cb:mulu><head>其二</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a20"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184b17"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0932a2001"><l>鑪冶只應憑陋巷<caesura/>富饒應不是豪家</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a21"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184b18"/><l><g ref="#CB15085"/>來雨歇茆堂外<caesura/>散在閑庭買落花</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a22"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185a01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">其三</cb:mulu><head>其三</head></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a23"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">自遣三首</cb:mulu><head>自遣三首</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a24"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185a03"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0932a2401"><l>古屋苔荒疾乍瘳<caesura/>前村林木覺先秋</l>
<pb ed="X" xml:id="X56.0949.0932b" n="0932b"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b01"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185a04"/><l>野塘日暮搘笻立<caesura/>雲自無依水自流</l></lg>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b02"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185a05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">其一</cb:mulu><head>其一</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b03"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185a06"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0932b0301"><l>講退時時學苦吟<caesura/>人間聲利<note n="0932b0301" resp="CBETA" type="add">已【CB】，巳【卍續】</note><app n="0932b0301"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">巳</rdg></app>無心</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b04"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185a07"/><l>水邊占得清閑景<caesura/>雨霽遙峰夜月深</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b05"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185a08"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">其二</cb:mulu><head>其二</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b06"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185a09"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0932b0601"><l>不惑年猶欠四年<caesura/>道情高趣恥前賢</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b07"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185a10"/><l>清風明月知多少<caesura/>謾學廬山種白蓮</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b08"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185a11"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">其三</cb:mulu><head>其三</head></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b09"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185a12"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">送僧</cb:mulu><head>送僧</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b10"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185a13"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0932b1001"><l>萬緣難繫自由身<caesura/>道性何妨學世人</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b11"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185a14"/><l>擬向東門贈離別<caesura/>長堤楊柳未成春</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b12"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185a15"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">庭竹</cb:mulu><head>庭竹</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b13"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185a16"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0932b1301"><l>移去羣花種此君<caesura/>滿庭寒翠更無塵</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b14"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185a17"/><l>暑天閑遶煩襟盡<caesura/>猶有清風借四鄰</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b15"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185a18"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">雞</cb:mulu><head>雞</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b16"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185b01"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0932b1601"><l>簷前棲息傍蒿叢<caesura/>風雨司晨爾有功</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b17"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185b02"/><l>鸚鵡無能憑<g ref="#CB02439"/>舌<caesura/>侯門翻得養金籠</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b18"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185b03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">送僧之金陵</cb:mulu><head>送僧之金陵</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b19"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185b04"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0932b1901"><l>金錫孤<g ref="#CB06078"/>問去程<caesura/>萋萋原草暮煙平</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b20"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185b05"/><l>六朝舊跡秦淮畔<caesura/>應感興亡聽水聲</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b21"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185b06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">出道場山途中作</cb:mulu><head>出道場山途中作</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b22"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185b07"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0932b2201"><l>獨下層巒景物秋<caesura/>依依雲木似相留</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b23"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185b08"/><l>孤舟曉汎平波去<caesura/>更為青山一轉頭</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b24"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185b09"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">將之霅溪寄別擇梧師</cb:mulu><head>將之霅溪寄別擇梧師</head>
<pb ed="X" xml:id="X56.0949.0932c" n="0932c"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0932c01"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185b10"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0932c0101"><l>白雲深處草堂閑<caesura/>曾伴支公薄暮還</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932c02"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185b11"/><l>獨上孤舟欲西去<caesura/>倚檣迴望只青山</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932c03"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185b12"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">寄淨慈寺悟真師</cb:mulu><head>寄淨慈寺悟真師</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932c04"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185b13"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0932c0401"><l>憶得涼宵宿上方<caesura/>靜吟閑話趣何長</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932c05"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185b14"/><l>別來音信無由寄<caesura/>目斷遙天鴈一行</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932c06"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185b15"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">次韻詶梵天闍梨</cb:mulu><head>次韻詶梵天闍梨</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932c07"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185b16"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0932c0701"><l>數峰殘雪對閑門<caesura/>世態悠悠莫可論</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932c08"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185b17"/><l>靜室禪餘忽相憶<caesura/>劃<g ref="#CB01926"/>孤坐到黃昏</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932c09"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185b18"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">溪居即事寄梵天闍梨</cb:mulu><head>溪居即事寄梵天闍梨</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932c10"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186a01"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0932c1001"><l>松竹森森獨掩扉<caesura/>塵中誰復愛忘機</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932c11"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186a02"/><l>蒼苔滿砌無人到<caesura/>猶感幽禽夜夜歸</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932c12"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186a03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">武康溪居即事寄寶印大師四首</cb:mulu><head>武康溪居即事寄寶印大師四首</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932c13"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186a04"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0932c1301"><l>偶來溪上縱閑吟<caesura/>泉石深藏便有心</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932c14"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186a05"/><l>莫擬他年訪幽跡<caesura/>白雲青嶂更難尋</l></lg>
<lb ed="X" n="0932c15"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186a06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">其一</cb:mulu><head>其一</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932c16"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186a07"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0932c1601"><l>月下猿聲水畔山<caesura/>臥聽吟望只宜閑</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932c17"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186a08"/><l>柴門不掩無來客<caesura/>時有精靈暫往還</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932c18"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186a09"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">其二</cb:mulu><head>其二</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932c19"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186a10"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0932c1901"><l>世路驅驅又白頭<caesura/>爭如閑臥絕他求</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932c20"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186a11"/><l>門前荒隴依依在<caesura/><g ref="#CB15156"/>折松枯盡列侯</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932c21"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186a12"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">其三</cb:mulu><head>其三</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932c22"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186a13"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0932c2201"><l>禪外相懷雪乍晴<caesura/>音書早<g ref="#CB15085"/>到柴扃</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932c23"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186a14"/><l>殘陽獨倚危樓望<caesura/>極目山光數點青</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932c24"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186a15"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">其四</cb:mulu><head>其四</head></cb:div></cb:div>
<pb ed="X" xml:id="X56.0949.0933a" n="0933a"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0933a01"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186a16"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">瑪瑙院居戲題三首</cb:mulu><head>瑪瑙院居戲題三首</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0933a02"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186a17"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0933a0201"><l>水邊閑臥萬緣休<caesura/>言欲無瑕行欲修</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0933a03"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186a18"/><l>草屋衡門任窮困<caesura/>屠龍終自勝屠牛</l></lg>
<lb ed="X" n="0933a04"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186b01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">其一</cb:mulu><head>其一</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0933a05"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186b02"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0933a0501"><l>湖光淡淡涵幽戶<caesura/>苔色依依滿破廊</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0933a06"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186b03"/><l>寂寞便同夫子廟<caesura/>更無流俗入焚香</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0933a07"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186b04"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">其二</cb:mulu><head>其二</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0933a08"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186b05"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0933a0801"><l>白傳湖西瑪瑙坡<caesura/>軒牕蕭灑瀁煙波</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0933a09"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186b06"/><l>講餘終日焚香坐<caesura/>毀譽榮枯柰我何</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0933a10"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186b07"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">其三</cb:mulu><head>其三</head></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0933a11"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186b08"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">予近卜居孤山之下友人元敏以四絕見嘲遂依韻和詶</cb:mulu><head>予近卜居孤山之下友人元敏以四絕見嘲
<lb ed="X" n="0933a12"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186b09"/>遂依韻和詶</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0933a13"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186b10"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0933a1301"><l>窮居<note n="0933a1301" resp="CBETA" type="add">已【CB】，巳【卍續】</note><app n="0933a1301"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">巳</rdg></app>躡黔婁跡<caesura/>孤島徒稱瑪瑙坡</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0933a14"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186b11"/><l>糗飯蔾羮且閑樂<caesura/>更無車馬暫經過</l></lg>
<lb ed="X" n="0933a15"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186b12"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">其一</cb:mulu><head>其一</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0933a16"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186b13"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0933a1601"><l>所棲幽致異人寰<caesura/>野艇秋歸碧浪間</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0933a17"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186b14"/><l>殘日淡煙凝望處<caesura/>參差樓閣認孤山</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0933a18"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186b15"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">其二</cb:mulu><head>其二</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0933a19"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186b16"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0933a1901"><l>煙波雲木映閑扉<caesura/>養病深棲是所宜</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0933a20"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186b17"/><l>便欲上生尋內院<caesura/>却因泉石住多時</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0933a21"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186b18"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">其三</cb:mulu><head>其三</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0933a22"/><lb ed="R101" n="0187a01"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0933a2201"><l>虗堂入夏講殘經<caesura/>不擊鐘聲擊鼓聲</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0933a23"/><lb ed="R101" n="0187a02"/><l>林下唯君問幽趣<caesura/>紀陽儀式近方成</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0933a24"/><lb ed="R101" n="0187a03"/><l><note place="inline">後漢董春字紀陽每升講堂鳴鼓三通余近斆焉</note></l></lg></cb:div>
<pb ed="X" xml:id="X56.0949.0933b" n="0933b"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0933b01"/><lb ed="R101" n="0187a04"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">其四</cb:mulu><head>其四</head></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0933b02"/><lb ed="R101" n="0187a05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">庭<g ref="#CB15112"/></cb:mulu><head>庭<g ref="#CB15112"/></head>
<lb ed="X" n="0933b03"/><lb ed="R101" n="0187a06"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0933b0301"><l>支遁放君真有意<caesura/>衛公憐汝太無端</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0933b04"/><lb ed="R101" n="0187a07"/><l>司晨守禦那堪用<caesura/>殷頂霜毛只好看</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0933b05"/><lb ed="R101" n="0187a08"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">寄天台守能上人</cb:mulu><head>寄天台守能上人</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0933b06"/><lb ed="R101" n="0187a09"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0933b0601"><l>台嶺林泉勝十洲<caesura/>忘機長往更無愁</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0933b07"/><lb ed="R101" n="0187a10"/><l>考盤高趣何人識<caesura/>招隱新題幾處留</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0933b08"/><lb ed="R101" n="0187a11"/><l>深夜定迴華頂月<caesura/>經年書斷海門秋</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0933b09"/><lb ed="R101" n="0187a12"/><l>誰知抱疾西湖上<caesura/>南望雲山想勝游</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0933b10"/><lb ed="R101" n="0187a13"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">寄所知</cb:mulu><head>寄所知</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0933b11"/><lb ed="R101" n="0187a14"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0933b1101"><l>寵辱不關念<caesura/>揚名日更新<caesura/>但憐吾道在</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0933b12"/><lb ed="R101" n="0187a15"/><l>寧顧謫官頻<caesura/>故國拋天外<caesura/>全家寄水濵</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0933b13"/><lb ed="R101" n="0187a16"/><l>堂空巢少鷰<caesura/>門冷謁無人<caesura/>直氣終干斗</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0933b14"/><lb ed="R101" n="0187a17"/><l>剛腸肯泣麟<caesura/>逍遙輕嗣立<caesura/>乾沒笑安仁</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0933b15"/><lb ed="R101" n="0187a18"/><l>愛主長思闕<caesura/>尋幽且養神<caesura/>伴閑初種竹</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0933b16"/><lb ed="R101" n="0187b01"/><l>出使舊埋輪<caesura/><g ref="#CB02439"/>舌終期斷<caesura/>民冤必為伸</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0933b17"/><lb ed="R101" n="0187b02"/><l>他年修史傳<caesura/>誰可繼清塵</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0933b18"/><lb ed="R101" n="0187b03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">題石壁山紹上人觀風亭</cb:mulu><head>題石壁山紹上人觀風亭</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0933b19"/><lb ed="R101" n="0187b04"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0933b1901"><l>界江千萬山<caesura/>石壁惟清幽<caesura/>中有忘機人</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0933b20"/><lb ed="R101" n="0187b05"/><l>超然樂巖丘<caesura/>創亭號觀風<caesura/>嘉景自成收</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0933b21"/><lb ed="R101" n="0187b06"/><l>群峯呈<g ref="#CB15085"/>碧<caesura/>長溪瀉寒流<caesura/>視聽足怡情</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0933b22"/><lb ed="R101" n="0187b07"/><l>萬事安能求<caesura/>甞言徂暑天<caesura/>登時疑清秋</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0933b23"/><lb ed="R101" n="0187b08"/><l>雲容既冷淡<caesura/>松韻還颼飀<caesura/>擾擾九衢塵</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0933b24"/><lb ed="R101" n="0187b09"/><l>誰知高靜游</l></lg></cb:div>
<pb ed="X" xml:id="X56.0949.0933c" n="0933c"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0933c01"/><lb ed="R101" n="0187b10"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0933c02"/><lb ed="R101" n="0187b11"/><cb:juan fun="close" n="45"><cb:jhead>閑居編第四十五</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
</cb:div></body></text></TEI>